urlText: Buses replace trains on parts of the T4 Eastern Suburbs & Illawarra Line

  • Trains run between Illawarra Line stations and the City Circle, making extra stops at St Peters and Erskineville. Change at Town Hall for express buses to Bondi Junction.

  • Trains run between Waterfall and Sutherland, and between Hurstville and the City Circle.
  • Some trains continue to run between the City and Waterfall until 11pm. The last direct train leaves Central at 22:11 and arrives Waterfall at 23:05.

  • Thursday from 9.50pm to 2.40am, buses replace trains between Cronulla and Sutherland.
  • Trains run between Waterfall and the City Circle.

  • South Coast Line trains continue to run, some to a changed timetable.

  • Richmond trains run between Richmond and Olympic Park only, making an extra stop at Granville. Change trains to continue your journey towards the City.
  • Penrith trains make an extra stop at Burwood.

  • From 10pm Saturday to 10am Sunday, buses replace trains between Strathfield and Central.
  • Penrith trains run between Penrith and Ashfield only, to a changed timetable.
  • Change at Strathfield for express and all-stations buses towards Central or remain on the train if you are travelling to Burwood, Croydon or Ashfield.

  • Trackwork also affects trains on the City Circle and T1 North Shore Line.

  • Replacement buses may be impacted by driver shortages. We are doing all we can to minimise the impact to your journey and provide a safe service, however cancellations or delays may occur.
  • Plan your trip before you travel for up-to-date real time information. You can also subscribe to planned trackwork alerts.

urlText: Station Update - Lidcombe
content:
From late night Friday 12 January to early morning Monday 15 January, there will be platform flooring upgrade works on Platform 4 at Lidcombe Station.

These works will be completed during the rail shutdown weekend, when there are no train services operating on this platform.

From Monday 15 January to Friday 2 February, about 80 metres of Platform 4 (from the Auburn end of the platform and continuing past the platform building) will have warning tactile progressively re-installed.

During this period, there will be support from pedestrian traffic controllers to guide customers around the area without tactile.

Please follow these staff directions.
